Definitely an improvement over the free version. Having extra players and two decks makes it more of a challenge and also makes it possible for players to rise and fall over rounds. Wish there was an option to control the number of cards that best and worst players have to swap, and also for how many standings points each place receives. Those are the only major gripes, however. Game play is rather smooth and there are plenty of other rules options to try.
